{
  "stem": "26983.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember that room we rented was a German moved in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the beginning--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning it was-- it wasn't taken.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still, in a way, normal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We rent the room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was a German woman, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Florian ?] was her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A very nice woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she was, in my eyes, an elderly woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe she was 35.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "35, 40.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because later on, her son came to visit us, a soldier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have a story about him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in the beginning, everything was more or less normal, but we were forbidden slowly to go to parks-- Jews and dogs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] are forbidden.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It came later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we were forbidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The park was written to Jew and dogs, Eintritt verboten.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's forbidden to go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go to cinemas or to swimming pools and other places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, there were rationalized the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Jews could only buy much later and only in certain shops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so when we came in the evening, we got only the leftovers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Still later, we didn't got the same rations like other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No milk and so on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "More and more restriction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then, there was a law.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had to give away all our jewelries and pets and bicycles and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but at that time, no many people had radios.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And more and more restriction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then there was something very strange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mahrisch-Ostrau was the very first city or town which evacuated, which there was a forced evacuation of Jews to Nisko.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was in '39.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nisko is in Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent all the Jews, about from 18 to 45 or something like that, had to register and were sent to Nisko.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
